Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.17,Flashback,Nobuaki narr,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.04,Flashback,Nobuaki narr,0,0,0,,Prepáč, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.34,Flashback,Ria,0,0,0,,Si hlúpy?
